snippet.title: Jousting Manager New UI Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2746150/Jousting_Manager?utm_source=youtube

Jousting Manager invites you to lead a medieval jousting team to glory. Scout, train and strategize to win diverse tournaments. Manage your team, plan seasons wisely, and emerge as the ultimate champion in this thrilling management simulation. Will you forge a legendary legacy?

Discord: https://discord.gg/TTNpPrhYS7
Twitter: https://twitter.com/joustingmanager
